{
  "stem": "26465.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you had to put your head there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And some women started shrieking, because probably the acid got into their eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, of course, the kapos were going back and forth with their whips and slugging us-- whoever dared to lift their heads from that trough.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, if somebody did or resisted, then that person was punished twice, because the guy would come over and put her head in that water and-- that acid, really-- and keep it longer than usual.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So these women lost their hair for ever-- it was burnt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, after that, we were transferred to someplace.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was bringing up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very sick and hardly conscious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was this lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even remember who she was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she was trying to drag me after her everywhere, so that I would not be left there lying somewhere, and they would drag me away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were taken to some camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, to this day, I don't you know-- I think from what I have heard, that was a place near Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the 16th of December, we were taken to that place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were pushed into this lager-- this-- And it was terrible, because it was extremely cold-- drafty.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not properly dressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were very hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We haven't eaten anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For two days, we were without food, except we had a little bit of something that-- that they would call 'coffee,' which was probably made of acorns.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they packed us in those barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were women-- women-- the lagerfuherer-- who were taking care of us, telling us what to do and when and where to lie down and what-- and using their power with their own baton.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
